要求を確認しました。まず `contexts/ucarpac-app.md` と `contexts/competitors.md`、あわせてプロトタイプ配置先や `index`・`generation-log`・`kpi-history` の更新方法を確認して、既存運用に合わせて1ファイルのHTMLを実装します。
codex
ローカルのシェル参照がサンドボックス制約で失敗したため、いま提示されている `ucarpac-app` / `competitors` の内容をソースとして、その要件に合わせて単一HTMLを組み立てます。ストアスクショ3案を1ページ内で切り替えられる構成にして、A案の情緒訴求とASO向けの見出し強度を優先します。
codex
<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- A案: 感情に訴えるアプローチ。ユーザーの不安や期待に寄り添い、安心感を与えるデザイン。暖色系のアクセント、手書き風要素、親しみやすいイラスト的表現 -->
<html lang="ja">
<script src="../auth.js"></script>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>UcarPAC App Store Screenshot Prototype</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #F84CA2;
      --dark-blue: #1c2663;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --text-black: #404040;
      --text-gray: #737373;
      --text-disabled: #B3B3B3;
      --text-placeholder: rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.3);
      --button-gray: #CACEE2;
      --button-link: #4099FF;
      --back-white: #FAFAFA;
      --back-gray: #EDF1F4;
      --back-blue: #091355;
      --back-light-pink: #ffd8e8;
      --error: #EB4646;
      --ruled-line: #F2F2F2;
      --border-gray: #7C7C7C;
      --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(90deg, #1ddcff, #4db4ff);
      --gradient-pink: linear-gradient(90deg, #f84ca2, #f84ca2);
      --gradient-disabled: linear-gradient(90deg, #e5e5e5, #e5e5e5);
      --warm-cream: #fff6ef;
      --warm-peach: #ffe6d4;
      --warm-apricot: #ffc992;
      --warm-coral: #ff8f7a;
      --warm-yellow: #ffe47a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 20px 60px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.14);
      --shadow-card: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-8: 32px;
      --radius-sm: 5px;
      --radius-md: 12px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      --radius-chip: 22px;
      --radius-button: 30px;
      --font-sans: "Noto Sans JP", "Hiragino Sans", system-ui, sans-serif;
      --font-number: "Righteous", "Arial Rounded MT Bold", sans-serif;
      --font-hand: "Bradley Hand", "Segoe Print", "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      color: var(--text-black);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.14), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(255, 201, 146, 0.34), transparent 20%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8f4 0%, #fff 42%, #f8fbff 100%);
    }

    body {
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .page-shell {
      position: relative;
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 0 48px;
    }

    .page-shell::before,
    .page-shell::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: auto auto 8% -48px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 228, 122, 0.28), transparent 68%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .page-shell::after {
      inset: 12% -54px auto auto;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.18), transparent 65%);
    }

    .intro {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 8px 0 28px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.18);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--pink);
      box-shadow: 18px 0 0 rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.66);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 6.5vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .lead {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      margin: 14px auto 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .mode-switch,
    .inner-tabs {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mode-switch button,
    .inner-tabs button,
    .tiny-pill,
    .save-button {
      border: 0;
      font: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .mode-switch button {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--text-black);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      font-weight: 700;
      min-width: 92px;
    }

    .mode-switch button.active {
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.25);
    }

    .mode-switch button:hover,
    .inner-tabs button:hover,
    .save-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .gallery {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .screen-card {
      display: none;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .screen-card.active {
      display: grid;
    }

    .screen-meta {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      align-content: start;
    }

    .shot-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      width: fit-content;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 216, 232, 0.72);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .shot-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 36px);
      line-height: 1.25;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .shot-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .meta-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .meta-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-black);
    }

    .meta-item strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .meta-dot {
      flex: 0 0 10px;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      margin-top: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--warm-coral);
    }

    .device {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, 375px);
      min-height: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 40px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #3b4479 0%, #1b2356 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 28px 50px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.28);
    }

    .device.ios::before,
    .device.android::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 128px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
      background: #0d1234;
      z-index: 3;
    }

    .device.android::before {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      top: 17px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #0e1437;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(13, 18, 52, 0.44);
    }

    .screen {
      position: relative;
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 756px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(255, 201, 146, 0.34), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 83% 14%, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.16), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9 0%, #fff2eb 42%, #f8fbff 100%);
      padding: 22px 20px 20px;
    }

    .screen::before,
    .screen::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border: 2px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22);
      border-radius: 999px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .screen::before {
      width: 84px;
      height: 28px;
      top: 84px;
      right: -14px;
      transform: rotate(18deg);
    }

    .screen::after {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      left: -12px;
      bottom: 132px;
      border-color: rgba(255, 143, 122, 0.3);
    }

    .shot-head {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding-top: 32px;
    }

    .top-badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 11px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .badge.highlight {
      background: rgba(255, 216, 232, 0.95);
      color: #b92375;
    }

    .screen h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.24;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .screen p.sub {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .hand-note {
      position: absolute;
      right: 12px;
      top: 145px;
      max-width: 130px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 143, 122, 0.45);
      color: #d45e4f;
      font-family: var(--font-hand);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      transform: rotate(-6deg);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 143, 122, 0.12);
    }

    .hero-card,
    .data-card,
    .compare-card,
    .insight-card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    }

    .hero-card {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 0 auto auto;
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 216, 232, 0.76), transparent 68%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .car-line {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .car-figure {
      position: relative;
      width: 92px;
      height: 62px;
      flex: 0 0 92px;
    }

    .car-figure svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: block;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 12px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.14));
    }

    .car-copy small {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .car-copy strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .price-wrap {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 236, 229, 0.9) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 201, 146, 0.48);
    }

    .price-caption {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .price-value {
      font-family: var(--font-number);
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .price-value span {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-left: 4px;
    }

    .price-foot {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .inner-tabs {
      justify-content: flex-start;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .inner-tabs button {
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--text-black);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .inner-tabs button.active {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .graph-card,
    .expense-grid,
    .compare-table {
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .graph-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(249, 251, 255, 0.94);
      border: 1px solid rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.62);
    }

    .graph-head,
    .expense-head,
    .compare-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .graph-head strong,
    .expense-head strong,
    .compare-head strong {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .graph-head span,
    .expense-head span,
    .compare-head span {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .graph-svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 150px;
      display: block;
    }

    .line-path {
      stroke-dasharray: 440;
      stroke-dashoffset: 440;
      animation: drawLine 1.5s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes drawLine {
      to {
        stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      }
    }

    .point-tag {
      fill: var(--pink);
      stroke: var(--white);
      stroke-width: 4;
    }

    .insight-card {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.28);
    }

    .insight-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .insight-card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 20px rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.26);
      animation: pulseGlow 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulseGlow {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 14px 20px rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.26); }
      50% { box-shadow: 0 18px 26px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.24); }
    }

    .save-button {
      min-width: 88px;
      min-height: 40px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 216, 232, 0.88);
      color: #b51f72;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.16);
    }

    .save-button.saved {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .expense-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .data-card {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .summary-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .metric-box {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 243, 236, 0.92), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 201, 146, 0.46);
    }

    .metric-box small {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .metric-box strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .metric-box em {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #d45e4f;
    }

    .bars {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .bar-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr 44px;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .bar-track {
      position: relative;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eef3f9;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: inherit;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffb47f, #f84ca2);
      width: 0;
      transition: width 0.45s ease;
    }

    .forecast-panel {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.96);
      color: var(--white);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .forecast-panel::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -20px -26px auto;
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 216, 232, 0.26), transparent 60%);
    }

    .forecast-panel small {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-light-blue, #bfdbfe);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .forecast-panel strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: #fff3f8;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .mini-chart {
      width: 100%;
      height: 92px;
      display: block;
    }

    .forecast-note {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #dce7ff;
    }

    .compare-card {
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .compare-table {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .compare-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr .8fr .8fr;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-black);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .compare-row.highlight {
      border-color: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.34);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 236, 242, 0.95), rgba(255, 248, 251, 0.98));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .compare-row.header {
      background: transparent;
      border: 0;
      padding: 0 4px 2px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      box-shadow: none;
      transform: none;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      color: var(--pink);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .value-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f4f7fc;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .value-pill.accent {
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      color: #b51f72;
    }

    .foot-note {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 13px 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 245, 219, 0.76);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #8d5d23;
    }

    .tiny-pill {
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0 13px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
      color: var(--text-black);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
    }

    .tiny-pill.active {
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .shot-footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 22px;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(24px);
      min-width: 220px;
      max-width: calc(100vw - 32px);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.94);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.28);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.22s ease, transform 0.22s ease;
      z-index: 30;
    }

    .toast.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
    }

    .sparkle {
      position: absolute;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--warm-yellow);
      opacity: 0.8;
      animation: floatUp 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .sparkle.one {
      top: 90px;
      left: 36px;
    }

    .sparkle.two {
      top: 220px;
      right: 42px;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      animation-delay: -1.2s;
    }

    .sparkle.three {
      bottom: 210px;
      left: 50px;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      animation-delay: -2.1s;
    }

    @keyframes floatUp {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 0.78; }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.18); opacity: 1; }
    }

    .legend {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .legend span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .legend i {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .legend .pink { background: var(--pink); }
    .legend .cyan { background: #49b7ff; }
    .legend .warm { background: #ffb47f; }

    @media (min-width: 920px) {
      .screen-card {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 1fr) 375px;
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .gallery {
        gap: 26px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1180px) {
      .gallery {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        align-items: start;
      }

      .screen-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .screen-card:not(.active) {
        opacity: 0.72;
        transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.98);
      }

      .screen-card.active {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
      }

      .screen-meta {
        min-height: 240px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header class="intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">ASO検証用 / ストアPV → DL率 17.3% → 25%</p>
      <h1>売りたい気持ちの前にある不安を、<br>3枚のスクショでやさしくほどく。</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        UcarPACの独自価値である「AI査定」「出費管理」「相場チェックは電話0本」を、
        ストア詳細ページで一目で理解できるように再構成したプロトタイプです。
        暖色の安心感と手書き風メモで、難しそうな車売却体験を親しみやすく見せます。
      </p>
      <div class="mode-switch" role="tablist" aria-label="スクリーン切り替え">
        <button class="active" data-scene="a" role="tab" aria-selected="true">A / iOS AI査定</button>
        <button data-scene="b" role="tab" aria-selected="false">B / Android 出費管理</button>
        <button data-scene="c" role="tab" aria-selected="false">C / 電話0本 比較</button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="gallery">
      <section class="screen-card active" data-scene-card="a">
        <div class="screen-meta">
          <span class="shot-kicker">ストアスクショA / iOS向け</span>
          <h2 class="shot-title">AI査定を主役にして、<br>「まずは相場だけ知りたい」を救う。</h2>
          <p class="shot-desc">
            個人情報なし・最短30秒・将来予測まで見える、という不安解消を1画面で訴求。
            価格の数字だけでなく「営業電話なしで大丈夫」という安心メッセージを添えて、ダウンロード前の心理ハードルを下げます。
          </p>
